				Cook-it by Seb/The Removers
				
				
	Welcome to this marvellous real-time renderer !!!!!!!!
	
	
	No, just joking !
	
	Well, do you know Videl Inside ?? Yes this splendid screen-blower !

	Cook-it was written to correct a little bug of Videl Inside v 1.2 .
	Indeed Videl Inside doesn't install properly his cookie in the cookie-jar and the bug
is apparent when you start for the first time your Falcon . You open the CPX 'Show-Cookie' and
you can see that the Cookie-jar is almost empty, because of the bug of VI .
	So what does Cook-it ??
	Cook-it checks if the Cookie-Jar exists :
		- if not, Cook-It create a Cookie-Jar and that's all !!
		- otherwise, Cook-it allows a new cookie-jar which could contain up to 256
		cookies and copys the current cookie-jar in it . Then he informs the system
		and that's all !!
	How to install ??
	Put Cook-It in your AUTO Folder before all the other programs .
	But what about Videl Inside ???
	No more problems . ( but if it continues to bug, put Cook-It just after Videl Inside
	in your AUTO folder )

							Have fun !
							
								Seb/The Removers .
								
	
